  • What is the price of PAX Gold today?

    Today, September 8, 2025, the price of PAX Gold (PAXG) is $3,641.99.

  • How do I add PAX Gold to MetaMask?

    MetaMask automatically displays popular tokens like PAX Gold（PAXG）within your wallet. If you are not seeing your PAXG in MetaMask, you can manually add it using the "Add to MetaMask" button above, over the price chart. Please remember that you first need to install MetaMask extension if you are on a PC or Mac (desktop computer). If you are on mobile, please check out our MetaMask Support guide here for more info.

  • How do I buy PAX Gold?

    Buying PAX Gold (PAXG) in MetaMask wallet is speedy, simple, and safe. You can buy PAX Gold (PAXG) tokens directly in MetaMask using payment methods like a credit card, debit card, bank account, Apple Pay, Google Pay, or PayPal. There’s no need for centralized exchanges. Select from thousands of your favorite tokens to buy on over 15 networks including Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Linea, Base, and more.

  • How do I sell PAX Gold?

    MetaMask makes it easy to sell your PAX Gold (PAXG) and convert your crypto to cash. You can exchange from MetaMask wallet directly to your debit card, credit card, PayPal, or bank account. By removing unnecessary steps and cutting excess fees, offramping your digital assets is fast and simple.

  • How do I swap PAX Gold?

    Swapping PAXG is simple and cost-effective with MetaMask. Choose from thousands of your favorite tokens across ten networks including Ethereum, Solana, Linea, Base, and Arbitrum. MetaMask Swaps also include gas fees right in your quotes, making swapping crypto as smooth as can be.

  • How do I bridge PAX Gold?

    Bridging crypto across chains allows you to move tokens from one network to another. With MetaMask, bridging PAX Gold (PAXG) is easy, secure, and cost-effective. Our aggregator finds the most efficient routes to move your digital assets from one chain to another. And with cross-chain swapping, bridging and swapping can take place at the same time in a single transaction. Meaning: instead of bridging PAXG from chain A and wrapping or unwrapping it on chain B, you can swap PAXG from chain A to a second token on chain B, all in one move.

  • What can you do with PAX Gold?

    With PAX Gold, you can send and receive PAXG, the network’s native token, and use it to pay transaction fees on certain networks. PAXG is supported in decentralized apps for trading, staking, yield optimization, and payments. You can participate in DeFi protocols, bridge assets between networks, or use PAXG in select web3 financial strategies, all with Ethereum-compatible speed and flexibility.

  • How do I trade PAX Gold for other cryptocurrencies?

    Trading PAX Gold (PAXG) for ETH, WBTC, or SOL can be done directly in MetaMask. For more information on how to swap PAXG, head to MetaMask Support.
